This directory contains files related to scoring grid construction.

                             --- * ---

script_demo     			Script to perform demonstration
nchemgrid_GB				Folder where grids for GB for Zou GBSA are calculated
nchemgrid_SA				Folder where grids for SA for Zou GBSA are calculated
nchemgrid_GB/INCHEM		Input parameters for NCHEMGRID_GB 
nchemgrid_GB/cavity.pdb	Cavity pdb file (empty)
nchemgrid_SA/INCHEM		Input parameters for NCHEMGRID_SA
gbsa_hawkins_grid.in		Input parameters for GRID for Hawkins GBSA
script_clean    			Script to remove files made by script_demo
